Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs100\bord1\c&H020000&\3c&H000000&\pos(532,854)}旱\N鴨\N子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:55.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有我一個人在海邊帶著游泳圈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 竟然是旱鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼樣都要去山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:12.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用四宮家的私人海灘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還配備溫水淋浴的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日曬可是少女的天敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就準備最高級的防曬霜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫上一流的按摩師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,肌膚的護理也得到了保障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會有鯊魚出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就雇用佛羅里達頂尖的獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯就吃魚翅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,萬惡的有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:42.57,Kaguya_xingkai,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(488,0)\fs60\3c&HECE8E6&\c&H23221F&\bord5}會長可能\N會說的事 \N{\fs50}VOL.四十二 \N{\fs80}旅行篇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為了應對會長反對的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:40.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經做好了應對手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你怎麼進攻都不會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊只能夏天去不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡氣候無常 還容易下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且蟲子還多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蟲子……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蟲子不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\an5\3c&H000000&\pos(466,512)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 140 500 l 140 0
