Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦去海邊的話不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山裡的話又有蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年的泳衣大小也不合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要買新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮對身材曲線很有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是算上這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮的攻擊力很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是玩具槍的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而相反藤原書記的攻擊力是戰車水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,戰力差距近乎絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:49.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說色誘 這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,相對而言四宮的該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可憐的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:07.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:09.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人又多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:10.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還可能有鯊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去山裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才的說法完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡經常下雨 還有蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:18.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:20.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:21.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:21.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:22.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 不如讓藤原書記決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！我決定嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊啊 去海邊 你懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡啊 去山裡 你不會背叛我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:38.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個裡面選的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:40.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:41.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說是去山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恐山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三途河畔的地獄溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多代表輪迴的風車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:02.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難得去一次 也讓巫女降死者的靈看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,選誰比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.01,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,基督 佛陀 聖德太子也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要不 等到夏天再考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:13.22,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,亞里士多德 莎士比亞 克利奧帕特拉 愛因斯坦 豐臣秀吉
